trans-unit.source: Contains instance information about a single instance of a <xref href="System.Windows.Data.PriorityBinding"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 단일 인스턴스에 대 한 인스턴스 정보를 포함 한 <xref href="System.Windows.Data.PriorityBinding"> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Data.PriorityBinding> is a single run-time instance of a PriorityBindingExpression.

Therefore, it describes a collection of <xref:System.Windows.Data.BindingExpression> objects that are attached to a single binding target property, which receives its value from the first <xref:System.Windows.Data.BindingExpression> object in the collection that returns a value successfully.
trans-unit.target: 따라서의 컬렉션을 설명 <xref:System.Windows.Data.BindingExpression>해당 값을 받는 첫 번째에서 단일 바인딩 대상 속성에 연결 된 개체 <xref:System.Windows.Data.BindingExpression>성공적으로 값을 반환 하는 컬렉션의 개체입니다.</xref:System.Windows.Data.BindingExpression> </xref:System.Windows.Data.BindingExpression>

trans-unit.source: For information about binding expressions, see the Binding and BindingExpression section in the [Data Binding Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: 바인딩 식에 대 한 정보에 바인딩 및 BindingExpression 섹션을 참조는 [데이터 바인딩 개요](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)합니다.

trans-unit.source: The binding engine determines which of the <xref:System.Windows.Data.BindingExpression> objects is the <xref:System.Windows.Data.PriorityBindingExpression.ActiveBindingExpression%2A> based on priority.
For more information, see <xref:System.Windows.Data.PriorityBinding>.
Gets the active <xref href="System.Windows.Data.BindingExpression"></xref> object.
The binding engine determines which of the <xref:System.Windows.Data.BindingExpression> objects is the ActiveBindingExpression based on priority.
trans-unit.target: 바인딩 엔진을 결정는 <xref:System.Windows.Data.BindingExpression>우선 순위에 따라 하는 ActiveBindingExpression 개체.</xref:System.Windows.Data.BindingExpression>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see <xref:System.Windows.Data.PriorityBinding>.

The active <xref href="System.Windows.Data.BindingExpression"></xref> object; or <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>, if no <xref href="System.Windows.Data.BindingExpression"></xref> object is active.
trans-unit.target: 활성 <xref href="System.Windows.Data.BindingExpression"> </xref> ; 개체 또는 <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>되지 않은 경우 <xref href="System.Windows.Data.BindingExpression"> </xref> 개체가 활성화 되어 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: Although the return type is <xref href="System.Windows.Data.BindingExpressionBase"></xref>, the returned object is only a <xref href="System.Windows.Data.BindingExpression"></xref> object because the <xref href="System.Windows.Data.PriorityBinding"></xref> class currently supports only <xref href="System.Windows.Data.Binding"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: 반환 형식이 있지만 <xref href="System.Windows.Data.BindingExpressionBase"> </xref>, 반환 된 개체는만 <xref href="System.Windows.Data.BindingExpression"> </xref> 때문에 개체는 <xref href="System.Windows.Data.PriorityBinding"> </xref> 클래스는 현재만 지원 <xref href="System.Windows.Data.Binding"> </xref> 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of <xref href="System.Windows.Data.BindingExpression"></xref> objects inside this instance of <xref href="System.Windows.Data.PriorityBindingExpression"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션을 가져옵니다 <xref href="System.Windows.Data.BindingExpression"> </xref> 의이 인스턴스 내에서 개체 <xref href="System.Windows.Data.PriorityBindingExpression"> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: A read-only collection of the <xref href="System.Windows.Data.BindingExpression"></xref> objects.

Although the return type is a collection of <xref href="System.Windows.Data.BindingExpressionBase"></xref> objects, the returned collection only contains <xref href="System.Windows.Data.BindingExpression"></xref> objects because the <xref href="System.Windows.Data.PriorityBinding"></xref> class currently supports only <xref href="System.Windows.Data.Binding"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: 반환 형식이의 컬렉션이 있지만 <xref href="System.Windows.Data.BindingExpressionBase"> </xref> 개체 반환된 된 컬렉션만 포함 <xref href="System.Windows.Data.BindingExpression"> </xref> 때문에 개체는 <xref href="System.Windows.Data.PriorityBinding"> </xref> 클래스는 현재만 지원 <xref href="System.Windows.Data.Binding"> </xref> 개체입니다.
